This directory contains a local Laplace hunt snapshot of pingora-pool 0.8.1,
originally distributed by Cloudflare, Inc. under the Apache License, Version 2.0.

The original Cloudflare copyright and Apache-2.0 license headers are preserved in
the vendored Rust sources. Laplace changes are limited to aliasing Tokio's
oneshot/watch/Notify and pingora-timeout seams to laplace-rt wrap-real hooks for
deterministic async exploration; the idle_poll I/O path is retained but excluded
from the model scope.

